Package: stringr.plus
Type: Package
Title: string functions that are "too specific for stringr" for Hadley Wickham
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("John", "Cassil", email = "john@johncassil.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A few handy functions for extracting strings before, after, and in between symbols. Works nicely for filenames and urls. Other wrapper functions may be included later.   
